------This is a geography quiz game.--------
---* For every correct answer, you will earn a point. *--------
-------For every wrong answer,you will lose a point,if you are wrong your point show your neigative point.-----------
-----------you will have the option of choosing between 4 multiple choice option.---------------
---------The objective of the game is to win above 7 points.if your total number of point are below 7,you lose.---------
*----------------------Good luck and have fun!---------------------------